subject: Basketball
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: This week, there was no upset for the Scarlet Knights, just despair as another chance to beat their nemesis, the Lady Vols, was pulled away in the final seconds of a 59-58 defeat.
